WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.200
How can you help my dad test drugs?

2
00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:03.600
Help my dad heal the soldiers

3
00:00:03.600 --> 00:00:05.966
Poison testing is likely to be either death or misery

4
00:00:05.966 --> 00:00:08.100
I still have important things to do recently

5
00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:09.100
Can't take the risk

6
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:10.900
My Shen family is poor and big

7
00:00:10.900 --> 00:00:14.000
I can help you with anything, but you can't help me

8
00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:17.133
Hey

9
00:00:27.333 --> 00:00:28.466
What are you doing?

10
00:00:29.266 --> 00:00:30.766
Who allowed you to enter my room?

11
00:00:30.766 --> 00:00:34.000
It seems that you are really obsessed with the emperor

12
00:00:34.733 --> 00:00:37.300
A king is a hero of a country, a world legend

13
00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:38.800
So what if I'm obsessed with him?

14
00:00:38.800 --> 00:00:41.233
How do you think I am better than him?

15
00:00:41.266 --> 00:00:42.666
Humph me

16
00:00:42.666 --> 00:00:45.166
You're nothing compared to him

17
00:00:45.166 --> 00:00:46.333
I'll tell you the truth

18
00:00:46.333 --> 00:00:48.200
I will only marry him in my life

19
00:00:48.200 --> 00:00:50.066
I advise you to give up

20
00:00:50.066 --> 00:00:51.933
He doesn't look down on you.

21
00:00:51.933 --> 00:00:53.166
Hmph, you are jealous

22
00:00:53.166 --> 00:00:54.200
As long as you are happy

23
00:00:54.200 --> 00:00:55.000
I'll go first

24
00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.233
Remember to make medicine for your dad

25
00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:03.500
Dad, what is the origin of that Qin Zhan?

26
00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.500
I don't know where he came from.

27
00:01:05.933 --> 00:01:06.900
Me

28
00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:10.200
I've been looking for him for years and haven't heard from him

29
00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:13.333
But he suddenly appeared

30
00:01:13.333 --> 00:01:15.766
So how do you know him?

